<p>Clicking this button runs the <code>post_to_clan.py</code> script for this specific post slug.</p>
<p>This script performs several actions:</p>
<ol>
    <li>Runs <code>npm run build</code> to ensure site files are up-to-date.</li>
    <li>Extracts the main article HTML content from the built site.</li>
    <li>Rewrites local image paths (<code>/images/...</code>) in the HTML to full public URLs (<code>https://static.clan.com/...</code>).</li>
    <li>Removes HTML comments from the content.</li>
    <li>Uploads the header image and all section images via the <code>uploadImage</code> API endpoint.</li>
    <li>Calls either the <code>createPost</code> or <code>editPost</code> API endpoint on Clan.com, sending post metadata and the processed HTML content.</li>
    <li>Updates the local <code>_data/syndication.json</code> file with the Clan.com Post ID upon successful creation.</li>
</ol>
<p>Monitor the "Action Log / Output" section below for detailed progress and any errors.</p>